<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="description" content="New Coding rest api workspace">
  <title>New Coding</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins:200,300,400,600,700,800" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;
      background: #0b0f19;
      color: #fff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(11, 15, 25, 0.75), rgba(11, 15, 25, 0.92)),
        url('https://pixhost.to/show/7353/717289326_img-20260422-wa0016.jpg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }
    .wrap {
      width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px 0 48px;
    }
    .nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 18px 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(17, 23, 35, 0.72);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }
    .brand {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-transform: lowercase;
    }
    .brand img {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    .navlinks {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .navlinks a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      font-size: 14px;
      text-transform: lowercase;
    }
    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr .85fr;
      gap: 22px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    .card {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(17, 23, 35, 0.74);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      padding: 30px;
    }
    h1, h2 {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      text-transform: lowercase;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 72px);
      line-height: .95;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.74);
      line-height: 1.8;
      text-transform: lowercase;
    }
    .label {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #00f2c3;
      text-transform: lowercase;
      letter-spacing: .14em;
    }
    .actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 48px;
      padding: 0 18px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: lowercase;
    }
    .primary {
      color: #07110f;
      background: #00f2c3;
    }
    .secondary {
      color: #fff;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }
    .list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .item {
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    }
    .item strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      text-transform: lowercase;
    }
    .bottom {
      margin-top: 22px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 920px) {
      .hero, .bottom {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <header class="nav">
      <div class="brand">
        <img src="https://pixhost.to/show/7353/717289326_img-20260422-wa0016.jpg" alt="New Coding">
        <span>New Coding</span>
      </div>
      <nav class="navlinks">
        <a href="/users/login">login</a>
        <a href="/users/register">register</a>
        <a href="/docs">dashboard</a>
        <a href="/pricing">pricing</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <article class="card">
        <span class="label">New Coding</span>
        <h1>rest api workspace yang simpel, gelap, dan enak dipakai.</h1>
        <p>
          isinya fokus ke fitur yang memang sering dipakai buat bot, tools, eksperimen, dan project harian. tidak ribet, tinggal masuk ke dashboard lalu pilih kategori yang dibutuhkan.
        </p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="button primary" href="/docs">masuk ke docs</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="/pricing">lihat pricing</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <aside class="card">
        <h2>isi utamanya</h2>
        <div class="list">
          <div class="item">
            <strong>downloader dan searching</strong>
            <p>buat kebutuhan endpoint yang sering dipakai sehari-hari.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <strong>animanga, random image, primbon</strong>
            <p>kategori tambahan biar project tidak perlu nyari source ke banyak tempat.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <strong>dashboard akun</strong>
            <p>buat lihat profil, api key, limit, premium, pricing, dan changelog.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="bottom">
      <article class="card">
        <h2>buat siapa</h2>
        <p>buat developer, owner bot, admin komunitas, atau siapa pun yang butuh api serbaguna dengan alur yang cepat.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>cara pakai</h2>
        <p>register, login, buka docs, ambil endpoint yang dibutuhkan, lalu lanjut ke project Anda.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>lanjutnya</h2>
        <p>kalau butuh limit lebih besar, tinggal cek pricing. kalau mau lihat update terbaru, buka changelog.</p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>

